 Mr Vally’s daughter stated that he walked out of his shop at around 10:00 on 28 May without saying a word. He also left his personal possessions, like his cellphone, in the store.
Mr Vally left in his vehicle, a silver Mercedes Benz C180 station wagon with registration plates: HHP137MP.  There was reason to suspect that Mr Vally was on his way to Middelburg, however, his family cannot confirm those statements.
A missing person’s case has been opened and everybody is asked to be on the look out for him.  Anyone who has seen him or has information on his whereabouts is urged to contact the Nelspruit Police or his family members at the following numbers:
